<div class="projects">

  <!-- PROJECT 1 -->
  <div class="project">
    <div class="project-meta">
      <span class="project-date">Jan 30, 2025</span>
      <span class="project-tag">Automation</span>
      <span class="project-tag">Python</span>
      <span class="project-tag">REST API</span>
    </div>
    <h2>ServiceNow incident data export to Excel</h2>
    <p class="project-intro">
      IT teams were losing hours each week manually extracting incident data from ServiceNow.
      This project automates that process end-to-end — from API authentication to a formatted
      Excel file — reducing extraction time from hours to seconds.
    </p>
    <div class="metrics">
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Records per run</div>
        <div class="metric-value">1,000+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Time saved</div>
        <div class="metric-value">~3h/week</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Manual errors</div>
        <div class="metric-value">Eliminated</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Solution overview</div>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">1</div><div class="step-t">Authenticates with the ServiceNow REST API using secure basic credentials</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">2</div><div class="step-t">Sends GET requests with custom query filters to the Incident Table</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">3</div><div class="step-t">Paginates automatically — no 100-record limit</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">4</div><div class="step-t">Parses JSON into a pandas DataFrame and exports to a formatted .xlsx file</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right-col">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title">Key challenge solved</div>
          <div class="challenge-text">The ServiceNow API limits responses to 100 records per call. This project implements automatic pagination — fetching all pages in sequence and merging them into a single clean dataset.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title">Tech stack</div>
          <div class="tech-pills">
            <span class="tech-pill">Python 3</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">requests</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">pandas</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">ServiceNow REST API</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">VS Code</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">.xlsx output</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="repo-btn" href="https://github.com/viviasantos/restapi-projects/tree/main/restapipy" target="_blank">
