  <hr class="project-divider"/>

  <!-- PROJECT 2 -->
  <div class="project">
    <div class="project-meta">
      <span class="project-date">May 20, 2025</span>
      <span class="project-tag">Integration</span>
      <span class="project-tag">ServiceNow</span>
      <span class="project-tag">REST Message</span>
    </div>
    <h2>ServiceNow to Jira integration via REST Message (P1 incidents)</h2>
    <p class="project-intro">
      Critical P1 incidents in ServiceNow required manual handoff to development teams in Jira,
      causing delays in response time. This project automates the bridge — the moment a P1 is
      created, Jira receives the data instantly via REST POST, with zero manual steps.
    </p>
    <div class="metrics">
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Trigger</div>
        <div class="metric-value">Automatic</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Notification delay</div>
        <div class="metric-value">~0s</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Manual steps</div>
        <div class="metric-value">Eliminated</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Solution overview</div>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">1</div><div class="step-t">Business Rule fires automatically on After Insert for new P1 incidents</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">2</div><div class="step-t">REST Message sends a POST with incident number, description, and priority as JSON</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">3</div><div class="step-t">Dynamic variable substitution injects live incident data into the payload</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-n">4</div><div class="step-t">Validated end-to-end using Webhook.site as a mock Jira endpoint</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right-col">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title">Key challenge solved</div>
          <div class="challenge-text">Business Rules require careful scoping to avoid infinite loops and performance issues. The trigger was scoped precisely to After Insert on P1 priority only, ensuring clean and reliable execution.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title">Tech stack</div>
          <div class="tech-pills">
            <span class="tech-pill">ServiceNow REST Message</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Business Rule</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Webhook.site</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">JSON</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">ServiceNow Studio</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Variable substitution</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
